8db0d96f860a07bbc554504a6e94b61546a6be22c0b9736c6b5aca628db9b618efc30609fce3702ee8e3812e1e34329c04d2f34bd69fdaecaa7c7fa0a2bde8a7  our-std-is-good-enough.patch
"
